WEBVTT


00:00:18.940 --> 00:00:23.880
ظآزOnly after bloom comes fruitظآز

00:00:25.290 --> 00:00:29.260
ظآزWho says glory must fade to the pastظآز

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:37.010
ظآزOnly through thunder
do you reach the cloudsظآز

00:00:38.210 --> 00:00:43.120
ظآزWho made you the crown of every peakظآز

00:00:44.650 --> 00:00:47.930
ظآزI stand at the center of the stageظآز

00:00:47.930 --> 00:00:51.000
ظآزMy shadow is pinned against the wallظآز

00:00:51.710 --> 00:00:56.660
ظآزFacing the light earns every medalظآز

00:00:57.700 --> 00:01:00.880
ظآزLittle birds,
save your needless peckingظآز

00:01:00.880 --> 00:01:04.160
ظآزThe open sky rises highظآز

00:01:04.700 --> 00:01:09.830
ظآزWhen night falls,
the moon begins to shineظآز

00:01:10.600 --> 00:01:13.860
ظآزI stand in the heart of these landsظآز

00:01:13.860 --> 00:01:17.220
ظآزMy shadow bears no crown or robeظآز

00:01:17.630 --> 00:01:23.300
ظآزThen I know truth needs no disguiseظآز

00:01:23.710 --> 00:01:26.960
ظآزThe green hills see me as I amظآز

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:30.290
ظآزLike dew, lightning,
and moon on the riverظآز

00:01:30.690 --> 00:01:34.730
ظآزShowing me exactly who I amظآز

00:01:34.730 --> 00:01:35.980
=The Lead=

00:01:36.020 --> 00:01:37.940
=Episode 25=

00:01:38.980 --> 00:01:40.160
What are the three characters?

00:01:40.600 --> 00:01:41.680
"Yi" as in memory.

00:01:42.200 --> 00:01:43.520
"Qin" is from Qinling Mountains.

00:01:44.520 --> 00:01:45.440
"E" stays the same.

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:47.080
They say

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:49.160
it's an ancient opera singer's name.

00:01:49.240 --> 00:01:51.680
And it means I miss my master.

00:01:53.640 --> 00:01:54.760
Did you agree to it?

00:01:55.840 --> 00:01:57.640
They just told me after they decided.

00:02:05.160 --> 00:02:06.520
I'll still call you Yi Qing'e.

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:12.026
You should call me Laidi.

00:02:18.240 --> 00:02:19.080
Okay.

00:02:41.520 --> 00:02:42.360
You...

00:02:43.640 --> 00:02:45.200
I'm leaving early tomorrow morning.

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:49.280
I'll see you off.

00:02:52.440 --> 00:02:53.813
My uncle told me to keep it quiet.

00:02:54.193 --> 00:02:55.620
He's afraid of people seeing us off.

00:03:23.520 --> 00:03:25.040
Keep your promise.

00:03:25.040 --> 00:03:26.306
Get into the provincial troupe.

00:03:27.800 --> 00:03:28.640
Okay.

00:03:33.920 --> 00:03:34.760
Okay.

00:03:36.560 --> 00:03:37.400
Okay.

00:03:38.560 --> 00:03:39.880
That's all you can say.

00:03:40.600 --> 00:03:42.080
Okay, okay, okay.

00:03:44.040 --> 00:03:45.080
I promise you.

00:03:51.720 --> 00:03:52.920
Play Orchid Grass for me.

00:04:05.520 --> 00:04:08.600
ظآزAutumn came soonظآز

00:04:08.600 --> 00:04:11.680
ظآزI moved the orchid indoorsظآز

00:04:11.680 --> 00:04:14.480
ظآزTending it day by dayظآز

00:04:14.480 --> 00:04:17.600
ظآزThinking of it night after nightظآز

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:20.680
ظآزWaiting for flowers to bloom in springظآز

00:04:20.680 --> 00:04:21.600
ظآزTo bloomظآز

00:04:24.440 --> 00:04:25.920
I forgot the lyrics.

00:04:28.520 --> 00:04:31.760
ظآزWaiting for flowers to bloom in springظآز

00:04:33.320 --> 00:04:36.080
ظآزTo fulfill my long-cherished wishظآز

00:04:39.440 --> 00:04:41.920
ظآزClusters of flowers filled the yardظآز

00:04:44.320 --> 00:04:46.560
ظآزAdding fragrance to the airظآز

00:05:35.760 --> 00:05:37.280
(That night,)

00:05:37.560 --> 00:05:39.440
(Yi Qin'e and Feng Xiaoxiao)

00:05:39.440 --> 00:05:41.120
(talked a lot.)

00:05:41.720 --> 00:05:44.040
(They talked about the troupe,
the provincial troupe,)

00:05:44.040 --> 00:05:46.360
(Chang'an, and her uncle,)

00:05:46.840 --> 00:05:49.040
(but they never said goodbye.)

00:05:50.520 --> 00:05:51.640
(When it was time to leave,)

00:05:52.200 --> 00:05:55.000
(Yi Qin'e and Feng Xiaoxiao both cried,)

00:05:55.640 --> 00:05:58.640
(hiding their tears from each other.)

00:05:59.920 --> 00:06:03.240
(The most important words were hidden)

00:06:03.440 --> 00:06:05.769
(Ningzhou County Qinqiang Opera Troupe)
(in the strings,)

00:06:05.780 --> 00:06:07.080
(the smiles,)

00:06:07.080 --> 00:06:11.560
(and the tears they secretly shed.)

00:06:47.140 --> 00:06:49.180
(Ningzhou County Qinqiang Opera Troupe)

00:07:01.080 --> 00:07:04.790
ظآزI came down from the mountainsظآز

00:07:04.790 --> 00:07:07.640
ظآزCarrying orchid grassظآز

00:07:08.470 --> 00:07:12.000
ظآزI planted it in my little gardenظآز

00:07:12.000 --> 00:07:15.280
ظآزHoping it would bloom soonظآز

00:07:15.980 --> 00:07:18.500
ظآزI checked on it three times a dayظآز

00:07:18.520 --> 00:07:20.880
The bus from Ningzhou to Chang'an

00:07:20.880 --> 00:07:21.893
is about to depart.

00:07:21.904 --> 00:07:23.602
(Ningzhou, Chang'an)
It's about to depart.

00:07:23.613 --> 00:07:25.720
Come on, move inside, let me through.

00:07:25.850 --> 00:07:26.840
Come on.

00:07:28.840 --> 00:07:29.920
- Sit tight.
- Over here.

00:07:29.920 --> 00:07:30.800
Sit tight.

00:07:31.960 --> 00:07:32.960
Bags are stowed.

00:07:34.080 --> 00:07:35.033
You should get off now.

00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:36.000
Don't block the way.

00:07:36.360 --> 00:07:37.440
The bus is leaving soon.

00:07:38.720 --> 00:07:39.560
Go back now.

00:07:39.840 --> 00:07:41.360
Put bags in the back, sir.

00:07:41.371 --> 00:07:43.177
(Ningzhou, Chang'an)
Don't put them on seats.

00:07:43.820 --> 00:07:45.760
- We're leaving soon.
- Put bags in the back row.

00:07:45.760 --> 00:07:46.600
In the very back.

00:07:47.230 --> 00:07:50.150
ظآزThinking of it night after nightظآز

00:07:50.900 --> 00:07:54.610
ظآزWaiting for flowers to bloom in springظآز

00:07:54.610 --> 00:07:57.980
ظآزTo fulfill my long-cherished wishظآز

00:07:58.400 --> 00:08:01.200
ظآزClusters of flowers filled the yardظآز

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:07.200
ظآزAdding fragrance to the airظآز

00:09:19.240 --> 00:09:20.160
Are you okay?

00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:24.240
If not, I'll tell the driver

00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:25.520
to pull over,

00:09:25.520 --> 00:09:26.520
so you can throw up.

00:09:28.120 --> 00:09:29.320
Sir, please pull over!

00:09:29.320 --> 00:09:30.446
Someone's about to throw up!

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:32.280
You think I can just stop?

00:09:32.280 --> 00:09:34.200
I can't just pull over
on a mountain road.

00:09:34.560 --> 00:09:36.246
If you don't,
they'll throw up in the car!

00:09:39.320 --> 00:09:40.360
So bumpy.

00:09:41.240 --> 00:09:42.120
Just hold it in.

00:09:52.720 --> 00:09:53.560
Stick your head out.

00:09:54.160 --> 00:09:55.000
Are you okay?

00:10:00.080 --> 00:10:01.120
Qin'e.

00:10:05.080 --> 00:10:06.120
He's everywhere.

00:10:09.220 --> 00:10:10.080
Look at this.

00:10:10.080 --> 00:10:11.480
Look what you did to my car!

00:10:11.760 --> 00:10:13.446
Do you know what the road ahead
is called?

00:10:13.840 --> 00:10:15.160
Sixty-Six Bends.

00:10:15.160 --> 00:10:16.320
It's also known as Sky Ladder.

00:10:16.800 --> 00:10:18.040
Even those who never get carsick

00:10:18.040 --> 00:10:19.040
can't handle this ride.

00:10:19.520 --> 00:10:20.840
Once this big bus starts up,

00:10:20.840 --> 00:10:22.140
we can't just pull over anywhere.

00:10:22.340 --> 00:10:23.210
If I let you on board,

00:10:23.210 --> 00:10:24.640
you'll throw up all over my bus.

00:10:24.880 --> 00:10:26.440
I'll use a bag to catch it.

00:10:27.200 --> 00:10:28.160
That won't do.

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:30.480
Go ride in your boyfriend's car.

00:10:30.491 --> 00:10:31.991
(Ningzhou, Chang'an)
I'll refund you.

00:10:33.120 --> 00:10:34.480
He's not my boyfriend.

00:10:35.050 --> 00:10:36.380
Uncle! Uncle!

00:10:37.440 --> 00:10:38.360
Just take my car.

00:10:38.840 --> 00:10:39.680
A small car like this

00:10:39.680 --> 00:10:41.400
is way more comfortable than a bus.

00:10:41.960 --> 00:10:42.800
On the way there,

00:10:42.800 --> 00:10:44.440
we can just roll the windows down.

00:10:44.880 --> 00:10:46.120
It'll be nice and breezy.

00:10:46.720 --> 00:10:48.160
You might not get carsick,

00:10:48.160 --> 00:10:49.360
but look at Qin'e.

00:10:49.680 --> 00:10:50.680
Look at the state of her.

00:10:51.120 --> 00:10:52.920
She represents the spirit of Ningzhou.

00:10:53.360 --> 00:10:54.180
When the leaders

00:10:54.191 --> 00:10:55.520
of the provincial troupe see her,

00:10:55.520 --> 00:10:56.360
it won't look good.

00:10:59.540 --> 00:11:02.780
(Qinchuan Qinqiang Opera Theater)

00:11:13.160 --> 00:11:15.640
- Qing!
- Bai!

00:11:15.720 --> 00:11:16.640
Jiahe,

00:11:16.640 --> 00:11:18.600
let's buy clothes
at Luoma Market tomorrow.

00:11:18.920 --> 00:11:20.800
I heard some new stores opened.

00:11:21.080 --> 00:11:22.400
They sell goods from Guangzhou

00:11:23.640 --> 00:11:25.160
in the latest Hong Kong (China) styles.

00:11:25.160 --> 00:11:26.160
Stop, stop!

00:11:26.160 --> 00:11:27.600
Shun! Shun!

00:11:29.120 --> 00:11:30.320
What's wrong with the lighting?

00:11:30.320 --> 00:11:31.200
It's too dark!

00:11:32.160 --> 00:11:33.000
The lighting?

00:11:38.560 --> 00:11:39.960
They aren't dark; they're fine.

00:11:39.960 --> 00:11:41.160
Or we'll lose the mood.

00:11:41.160 --> 00:11:43.400
We can't see the actors' expressions.

00:11:43.400 --> 00:11:44.760
Is the audience here for the mood

00:11:44.760 --> 00:11:46.360
or the actors' performances?

00:11:46.360 --> 00:11:47.480
Both.

00:11:49.000 --> 00:11:51.200
You stage crew guys

00:11:51.200 --> 00:11:52.320
always have so many issues.

00:11:52.840 --> 00:11:53.920
I stayed up all night,

00:11:53.920 --> 00:11:55.240
yet I'm still with you here.

00:11:55.240 --> 00:11:56.360
Why so many complaints?

00:11:56.920 --> 00:11:58.360
To me, the director

00:11:58.360 --> 00:11:59.840
is the embodiment of justice.

00:11:59.840 --> 00:12:00.800
He's never wrong.

00:12:01.120 --> 00:12:02.120
Just listen to him.

00:12:02.120 --> 00:12:03.120
You shut up.

00:12:03.520 --> 00:12:05.440
You guys are getting so demanding.

00:12:05.960 --> 00:12:06.800
Right, Director?

00:12:07.120 --> 00:12:09.000
You played mahjong
all night again, right?

00:12:10.000 --> 00:12:11.560
What mahjong?

00:12:11.560 --> 00:12:13.120
I was playing the drums.

00:12:16.080 --> 00:12:16.920
Qin'e,

00:12:17.480 --> 00:12:18.440
how are you feeling?

00:12:18.960 --> 00:12:21.040
This car is pretty steady, right?

00:12:21.040 --> 00:12:21.960
Do you feel better?

00:12:24.313 --> 00:12:25.433
Why not listen to the radio?

00:12:31.000 --> 00:12:32.120
Bai She Zhuan.

00:12:36.880 --> 00:12:37.720
Uncle.

00:12:37.920 --> 00:12:39.160
After 20 li ahead,

00:12:39.160 --> 00:12:40.320
we'll reach Shenquan County.

00:12:40.800 --> 00:12:42.760
They have a local specialty there.

00:12:42.760 --> 00:12:44.240
The Hanshui noodles are really good.

00:12:44.520 --> 00:12:45.600
I'll take you to try some.

00:12:51.160 --> 00:12:53.440
Uncle, what happened to your face?

00:12:54.800 --> 00:12:55.640
Why do you ask?

00:12:55.840 --> 00:12:56.680
Nothing.

00:12:57.320 --> 00:12:58.160
Just curious.

00:13:00.160 --> 00:13:02.600
A hospital in Chang'an treats scars.

00:13:03.080 --> 00:13:04.880
I can have my buddy contact them for us.

00:13:10.080 --> 00:13:11.760
You've followed us
since Ningzhou, right?

00:13:11.760 --> 00:13:12.880
Looking for an opportunity.

00:13:14.120 --> 00:13:16.560
Playing tactics,
offering help in a pinch.

00:13:16.873 --> 00:13:17.880
I don't know any tactics.

00:13:18.040 --> 00:13:19.100
But I used to be a soldier.

00:13:19.560 --> 00:13:21.760
I obey commands and follow orders.

00:13:23.080 --> 00:13:24.600
So, here's my order:

00:13:25.520 --> 00:13:26.360
From this moment on,

00:13:26.840 --> 00:13:28.560
keep your mouth shut.

00:13:29.320 --> 00:13:30.440
No resting halfway.

00:13:31.080 --> 00:13:33.160
Head to Chang'an at full speed.

00:13:33.640 --> 00:13:36.600
Yes, sir! Obeying orders,
marching forward!

00:13:41.120 --> 00:13:41.960
What's wrong?

00:13:42.040 --> 00:13:43.480
Wait, wait, stop for a second.

00:13:43.480 --> 00:13:44.960
- How could I forget?
- She'll puke!

00:13:45.520 --> 00:13:46.480
Stop, stop.

00:13:49.160 --> 00:13:50.080
Shen Yun,

00:13:50.080 --> 00:13:51.760
I've told you so many times.

00:13:52.040 --> 00:13:55.200
It's not pronounced

00:13:55.200 --> 00:13:57.840
like that.

00:13:58.160 --> 00:14:01.320
You make this line
sound incredibly tacky.

00:14:01.320 --> 00:14:02.320
No, I don't.

00:14:02.320 --> 00:14:03.560
Yes, you do.

00:14:03.560 --> 00:14:05.120
Come on, sing it without music.

00:14:08.440 --> 00:14:13.160
The heartless man is
the root of all disasters.

00:14:13.160 --> 00:14:14.000
See?

00:14:15.320 --> 00:14:16.400
Come on, read it once.

00:14:18.560 --> 00:14:22.880
The heartless man is
the root of all disasters.

00:14:24.320 --> 00:14:25.680
B-E-N, ben.

00:14:25.760 --> 00:14:27.000
B-E-N-G, beng.

00:14:27.400 --> 00:14:28.240
Oh, my.

00:14:28.480 --> 00:14:30.200
G-E-N, gen.

00:14:30.200 --> 00:14:31.200
G-E-N-G, geng.

00:14:33.780 --> 00:14:35.700
(For the provincial troupe)
We were engaged.

00:14:35.711 --> 00:14:36.640
(Shen Yun abandoned me)

00:14:36.640 --> 00:14:38.120
(Ungrateful)
Then we got married.

00:14:38.120 --> 00:14:40.560
She was at County Troupe;
I was at Rubber Factory.

00:14:40.873 --> 00:14:42.600
I paid the bride price
when we got married.

00:14:42.600 --> 00:14:43.540
- Enough.
- For...

00:14:43.800 --> 00:14:45.520
Stop standing here. It's been days.

00:14:46.040 --> 00:14:47.760
Leave now.
You're disrupting our work here.

00:14:47.760 --> 00:14:48.680
I didn't go inside.

00:14:48.680 --> 00:14:49.880
Why can't I stand here?

00:14:50.280 --> 00:14:51.120
This is a workplace.

00:14:51.120 --> 00:14:53.006
I don't work here;
you can't boss me around.

00:14:53.017 --> 00:14:54.995
- Shen Yun is my wife.
- You're disrupting work.

00:14:55.006 --> 00:14:55.840
(Rou Jia Mo)

00:14:55.840 --> 00:14:57.160
You guys tell me who's right!

00:14:57.720 --> 00:14:58.560
Troupe Leader!

00:14:59.320 --> 00:15:00.640
The troupe leader is back!

00:15:01.040 --> 00:15:02.600
The troupe leader is back!

00:15:02.600 --> 00:15:03.440
Troupe Leader!

00:15:03.760 --> 00:15:04.920
Troupe Leader!

00:15:04.920 --> 00:15:05.840
Help me out!

00:15:05.840 --> 00:15:07.120
I've told you already.

00:15:07.720 --> 00:15:08.880
This issue

00:15:08.880 --> 00:15:10.020
is a family dispute.

00:15:10.031 --> 00:15:11.722
You should go
to the Civil Affairs Bureau.

00:15:11.733 --> 00:15:13.440
Why come here?

00:15:13.760 --> 00:15:15.560
You have a job in Qianzhou.

00:15:15.560 --> 00:15:16.640
Why not hurry back to work?

00:15:16.640 --> 00:15:17.880
Why are you loitering here?

00:15:18.400 --> 00:15:19.960
Troupe Leader, if this isn't solved,

00:15:19.960 --> 00:15:21.800
my work can't get done!

00:15:21.800 --> 00:15:23.320
How is this not your business?

00:15:23.320 --> 00:15:25.560
If you hadn't moved her to Chang'an,

00:15:25.560 --> 00:15:26.960
she wouldn't have divorced me.

00:15:26.960 --> 00:15:28.320
Troupe Leader, please help me out.

00:15:28.320 --> 00:15:30.160
I'll do anything to avoid a divorce.

00:15:30.160 --> 00:15:31.040
That's nonsense.

00:15:31.200 --> 00:15:32.280
Divorce will happen

00:15:32.280 --> 00:15:33.760
if it's meant to.

00:15:33.760 --> 00:15:36.300
It's not about the provincial troupe,
right?

00:15:36.320 --> 00:15:37.240
Can you step aside?

00:15:37.240 --> 00:15:38.080
Troupe Leader!

00:15:38.560 --> 00:15:39.440
Stop pulling me.

00:15:39.440 --> 00:15:40.880
I'll call the cops if you do.

00:15:42.010 --> 00:15:42.880
Go.

00:15:43.070 --> 00:15:44.720
- Help, Troupe Leader!
- Close the door.

00:15:44.720 --> 00:15:46.120
Don't let random people in.

00:15:46.120 --> 00:15:46.960
Don't worry.

00:15:47.190 --> 00:15:48.040
- Go.
- But...

00:15:48.040 --> 00:15:49.720
- Nothing to see here!
- Troupe Leader!

00:15:49.720 --> 00:15:50.560
Back to work.

00:15:50.760 --> 00:15:51.600
Go ahead.

00:15:53.360 --> 00:15:54.360
Shen Yun!

00:15:54.920 --> 00:15:56.400
Come out, Shen Yun!

00:15:57.320 --> 00:15:58.200
Director Feng,

00:15:58.200 --> 00:15:59.440
is this ever going to end?

00:15:59.440 --> 00:16:00.520
Are we still rehearsing?

00:16:02.760 --> 00:16:03.600
Director,

00:16:03.920 --> 00:16:05.480
Shen Yun has some family issues,

00:16:05.480 --> 00:16:06.920
so she's not in a good mood.

00:16:06.920 --> 00:16:08.600
Why don't you let her take a break?

00:16:08.600 --> 00:16:09.640
I'll fill in for her.

00:16:10.680 --> 00:16:11.920
B-E-N, ben.

00:16:12.400 --> 00:16:13.640
G-E-N, gen.

00:16:14.740 --> 00:16:18.720
The heartless man is
the root of all disasters.

00:16:24.680 --> 00:16:26.000
Chu Jiahe, Shen Yun.

00:16:26.400 --> 00:16:27.440
Step down.

00:16:27.880 --> 00:16:29.840
Swap your costumes.

00:16:36.760 --> 00:16:37.600
Go.

00:17:37.240 --> 00:17:38.080
Just eat a little.

00:17:38.840 --> 00:17:40.400
You can't stay on an empty stomach.

00:17:40.400 --> 00:17:41.720
It'll make your stomach hurt more.

00:17:42.560 --> 00:17:43.400
Come on.

00:17:43.640 --> 00:17:44.480
Here, take this.

00:17:46.800 --> 00:17:48.040
We left early this morning

00:17:48.400 --> 00:17:50.080
and haven't eaten anything.

00:17:51.200 --> 00:17:52.240
You just threw up.

00:17:52.920 --> 00:17:53.760
Eat something.

00:18:18.880 --> 00:18:19.840
Why are you stopping?

00:18:23.600 --> 00:18:24.600
Why stop here?

00:18:25.360 --> 00:18:26.520
They sell food here.

00:18:28.400 --> 00:18:29.240
Uncle.

00:18:29.960 --> 00:18:32.000
Aren't we going too far?

00:18:36.400 --> 00:18:37.920
He didn't even ask me for it.

00:18:38.880 --> 00:18:40.080
Why force it on him?

00:18:42.440 --> 00:18:43.280
Only this?

00:18:43.600 --> 00:18:44.480
Got anything else?

00:18:44.480 --> 00:18:45.320
No.

00:18:50.240 --> 00:18:51.080
Qin'e,

00:18:51.640 --> 00:18:52.560
want some sour jujube?

00:18:53.400 --> 00:18:54.240
It's appetizing.

00:18:54.560 --> 00:18:55.400
Hey.

00:18:55.560 --> 00:18:57.280
How far are we from Chang'an?

00:18:57.760 --> 00:18:58.640
Three hours.

00:18:59.920 --> 00:19:00.920
Given Qin'e's condition,

00:19:01.097 --> 00:19:02.246
it'll take five to six hours.

00:19:02.400 --> 00:19:03.400
Why so long?

00:19:03.800 --> 00:19:05.160
It'll get dark when we get there.

00:19:05.720 --> 00:19:06.560
That's fine.

00:19:07.000 --> 00:19:08.000
I know Chang'an well.

00:19:08.000 --> 00:19:08.960
I'll handle everything.

00:19:09.640 --> 00:19:10.920
No need for that.

00:19:11.440 --> 00:19:13.926
Qin'e is the lead invited
by the provincial troupe.

00:19:13.937 --> 00:19:15.280
They've made all the arrangements.

00:19:15.280 --> 00:19:16.600
A telegram's been sent.

00:19:16.600 --> 00:19:17.873
We can't show up late on Day 1.

00:19:17.884 --> 00:19:18.980
It'd leave a bad impression.

00:19:18.980 --> 00:19:20.800
- No problem.
- Qin'e, where are you going?

00:19:21.120 --> 00:19:22.240
To relieve myself.

00:19:23.000 --> 00:19:23.840
I'll go with you.

00:19:24.400 --> 00:19:25.320
I know the way.

00:19:25.320 --> 00:19:26.160
Get back here.

00:19:27.160 --> 00:19:28.280
You know the way?

00:19:28.720 --> 00:19:30.160
You're talking nonsense.

00:19:30.400 --> 00:19:31.240
Here.

00:19:33.220 --> 00:19:35.620
(Peony Pavilion)

00:19:35.800 --> 00:19:37.480
Be careful and stay safe.

00:19:37.800 --> 00:19:39.120
Don't fall into the ditch.

00:19:49.050 --> 00:19:51.930
Why did you deceive my sister

00:19:51.930 --> 00:19:53.920
and sneak to Jinshan Temple?

00:19:53.920 --> 00:19:55.730
Tell me!

00:19:57.080 --> 00:19:58.490
- Troupe Leader.
- Speak.

00:19:58.710 --> 00:20:00.000
Xiao Qing, it's all...

00:20:00.000 --> 00:20:00.870
Shut up!

00:20:01.270 --> 00:20:03.680
If you hadn't believed Fahai's lies,

00:20:03.680 --> 00:20:06.240
- why would my sister suffer?
- Troupe Leader?

00:20:06.240 --> 00:20:07.860
You ungrateful wretch!

00:20:07.920 --> 00:20:09.820
- Here to see you rehearse.
- Why stay alive?

00:20:09.820 --> 00:20:10.750
- What's there
- Dear!

00:20:10.750 --> 00:20:12.040
- to see?
- Qing!

00:20:12.040 --> 00:20:14.840
It's not a key project like You Xi Hu.

00:20:15.360 --> 00:20:17.520
What are you talking about?

00:20:17.520 --> 00:20:18.880
Everyone knows

00:20:18.880 --> 00:20:20.120
that your Bai She Zhuan

00:20:20.120 --> 00:20:22.160
is a warm-up for You Xi Hu.

00:20:22.160 --> 00:20:23.160
Your Qing and Bai

00:20:23.171 --> 00:20:25.050
- are A and B roles for Li Hui Niang.
- Honey!

00:20:25.050 --> 00:20:26.000
Dear!

00:20:26.000 --> 00:20:28.840
That's why everyone is working so hard.

00:20:30.080 --> 00:20:31.626
Where's Director Gu? Why isn't he here?

00:20:32.400 --> 00:20:33.720
It's your play; why would he come?

00:20:35.720 --> 00:20:37.280
Okay, stop, stop.

00:20:38.400 --> 00:20:39.880
Alright, let's take a break.

00:20:39.880 --> 00:20:40.720
Troupe Leader.

00:20:41.840 --> 00:20:42.800
Good singing.

00:20:44.440 --> 00:20:46.480
I went to Ms. Li's house yesterday.

00:20:46.480 --> 00:20:47.320
We talked

00:20:47.320 --> 00:20:49.120
about us rehearsing You Xi Hu.

00:20:49.120 --> 00:20:50.600
She was so thrilled.

00:20:50.880 --> 00:20:52.960
Thank her for still thinking of us.

00:20:53.760 --> 00:20:54.720
How's her health?

00:20:54.960 --> 00:20:55.800
She's doing great.

00:20:56.640 --> 00:20:57.840
Good. Health is what matters.

00:20:58.280 --> 00:20:59.520
- Get some rest.
- Okay, sure.

00:21:03.960 --> 00:21:05.160
In the mountains,

00:21:05.160 --> 00:21:06.480
she was the lead.

00:21:06.840 --> 00:21:08.880
Now, she's an extra playing a maid.

00:21:08.880 --> 00:21:09.720
What is she after?

00:21:10.120 --> 00:21:11.400
You just don't get it.

00:21:11.400 --> 00:21:12.600
She's in the city now.

00:21:12.600 --> 00:21:13.950
Her status has changed too.

00:21:13.950 --> 00:21:14.920
Right?

00:21:14.920 --> 00:21:17.080
Qin Xianglian divorced Chen Shimei.

00:21:17.880 --> 00:21:19.720
Why don't you divorce Pi Liang?

00:21:20.000 --> 00:21:20.840
Get lost.

00:21:21.480 --> 00:21:22.720
Have some walnuts.

00:21:22.720 --> 00:21:24.360
My mom brought them from Ningzhou.

00:21:24.360 --> 00:21:25.200
Thanks.

00:21:28.240 --> 00:21:30.760
Have some walnuts. Good for the brain.

00:21:41.680 --> 00:21:43.360
Just spit it out.

00:21:45.960 --> 00:21:48.200
I just wanted to discuss You Xi Hu

00:21:48.480 --> 00:21:49.600
with you.

00:21:54.240 --> 00:21:57.760
Since Director Gu has his own ideas,

00:21:57.760 --> 00:22:00.200
and the troupe hired him for You Xi Hu

00:22:00.200 --> 00:22:02.040
as the traditional opera consultant,

00:22:02.320 --> 00:22:04.400
he can just make the calls himself.

00:22:04.400 --> 00:22:06.080
Why discuss it with me?

00:22:07.280 --> 00:22:09.200
Take it easy.

00:22:10.560 --> 00:22:11.920
We put the two of you

00:22:11.920 --> 00:22:13.080
together,

00:22:13.080 --> 00:22:14.920
hoping your ideas

00:22:14.920 --> 00:22:16.280
would clash.

00:22:16.800 --> 00:22:18.680
What if it sparks something new?

00:22:19.000 --> 00:22:19.840
Right?

00:22:20.640 --> 00:22:22.320
Besides,

00:22:22.320 --> 00:22:23.200
our Gong Lili

00:22:23.760 --> 00:22:25.560
is quite famous,

00:22:26.400 --> 00:22:28.440
and she's Ms. Li's last disciple.

00:22:28.440 --> 00:22:30.040
Whose last disciple she is

00:22:30.040 --> 00:22:31.560
has nothing to do with it.

00:22:32.000 --> 00:22:33.760
You've seen everyone in the troupe.

00:22:33.760 --> 00:22:36.400
She's the only one fit for this role.

00:22:36.400 --> 00:22:38.040
What's the core of this play?

00:22:38.320 --> 00:22:39.840
The character.

00:22:40.920 --> 00:22:41.760
Right?

00:22:42.080 --> 00:22:42.920
Right, right.

00:22:45.320 --> 00:22:46.520
Director. Troupe Leader.

00:22:46.520 --> 00:22:47.360
Have some walnuts.

00:22:47.640 --> 00:22:49.640
My mom sent them from Ningzhou.

00:22:50.120 --> 00:22:50.960
Thank you.

00:22:52.560 --> 00:22:54.240
You've been singing really well lately.

00:22:54.240 --> 00:22:55.080
Look.

00:22:55.200 --> 00:22:57.720
Her accent and vocals have improved.

00:22:57.720 --> 00:22:59.280
- Much better.
- Keep practicing.

00:22:59.280 --> 00:23:00.680
Give it a little more time.

00:23:00.680 --> 00:23:02.680
That out-of-town accent will be gone.

00:23:02.680 --> 00:23:04.080
Got it. Thank you, Troupe Leader.

00:23:04.840 --> 00:23:06.640
Have you sung Bai She Zhuan before?

00:23:09.200 --> 00:23:10.400
I sang it in Ningzhou before.

00:23:10.760 --> 00:23:11.920
You're from Ningzhou too?

00:23:12.880 --> 00:23:13.720
What a coincidence!

00:23:14.720 --> 00:23:16.360
When will Director Gu's pick arrive?

00:23:17.720 --> 00:23:18.680
Probably on the way.

00:23:19.960 --> 00:23:20.800
Chu Jiahe.

00:23:21.360 --> 00:23:22.280
Chu Jiahe,

00:23:22.920 --> 00:23:24.400
for tonight's performance,

00:23:24.400 --> 00:23:25.680
you'll play Qing.

00:23:28.866 --> 00:23:29.880
What are you waiting for?

00:23:29.880 --> 00:23:30.720
Get ready!

00:23:47.040 --> 00:23:47.880
Xu Xian!

00:23:48.760 --> 00:23:54.000
Why go to Jinshan Temple
behind my sister's back?

00:23:54.720 --> 00:23:55.920
Tell me!

00:23:58.560 --> 00:23:59.760
Speak!

00:24:00.780 --> 00:24:04.940
(Peony Pavilion)

00:24:06.480 --> 00:24:07.360
Liu Hongbing!

00:24:10.680 --> 00:24:11.640
Where is this guy?

00:24:13.560 --> 00:24:14.520
This fool...

00:24:18.880 --> 00:24:20.800
You shameless jerk!

00:24:20.800 --> 00:24:22.720
- What are you looking at?
- What?

00:24:22.720 --> 00:24:24.133
- You fool.
- Uncle, what's wrong?

00:24:24.144 --> 00:24:25.362
- You shameless creep!
- I...

00:24:25.373 --> 00:24:26.200
What are you doing?

00:24:26.200 --> 00:24:27.440
How am I shameless?

00:24:27.440 --> 00:24:28.320
You tell me!

00:24:28.380 --> 00:24:29.450
- I...
- Uncle!

00:24:32.080 --> 00:24:32.920
Why are you here?

00:24:33.040 --> 00:24:34.360
I relieved myself over there.

00:24:36.480 --> 00:24:37.320
Are you okay?

00:24:37.440 --> 00:24:38.280
I'm fine.

00:24:40.560 --> 00:24:42.080
What kind of guy do you think I am?

00:24:42.400 --> 00:24:44.320
What else?
Why was your butt sticking up?

00:24:44.800 --> 00:24:46.700
I saw a hedgehog on the road.

00:24:46.711 --> 00:24:48.400
I thought it might get run over
by a car,

00:24:48.400 --> 00:24:50.080
so I brought it here to let it go.

00:24:50.760 --> 00:24:52.880
You had to let it go here?

00:24:52.880 --> 00:24:53.760
You could let it go

00:24:53.760 --> 00:24:54.600
anywhere else!

00:24:54.960 --> 00:24:56.000
You shameless creep!

00:24:57.080 --> 00:24:58.120
Go, go.

00:24:58.680 --> 00:24:59.520
Hurry, hurry.

00:24:59.920 --> 00:25:00.760
Hurry up.

00:25:02.720 --> 00:25:03.560
Uncle Sanyuan,

00:25:03.880 --> 00:25:04.720
just listen to me.

00:25:05.240 --> 00:25:06.280
Before Qin'e

00:25:06.280 --> 00:25:07.560
marries me,

00:25:07.560 --> 00:25:08.760
I promise

00:25:08.760 --> 00:25:10.360
I won't do anything that Qin'e

00:25:10.360 --> 00:25:11.760
doesn't want me to do.

00:25:13.440 --> 00:25:14.360
Come on, come on.

00:25:15.160 --> 00:25:16.000
Watch your head.

00:25:18.360 --> 00:25:19.720
Qin'e, listen to me.

00:25:20.360 --> 00:25:21.200
You see...

00:25:25.400 --> 00:25:26.800
You feel bad that I haven't eaten,

00:25:27.360 --> 00:25:28.880
so you gave me a Mo.

00:25:30.800 --> 00:25:32.160
The Mo is so soft.

00:25:38.040 --> 00:25:40.800
Qin'e is so considerate.

00:25:41.640 --> 00:25:42.560
Seeing that I'm hungry,

00:25:43.160 --> 00:25:44.320
she gave me a Mo.

00:25:46.280 --> 00:25:47.120
So good.

00:25:56.360 --> 00:25:58.520
Your old name was Laidi?

00:26:01.920 --> 00:26:03.200
Your current name is better.

00:26:03.720 --> 00:26:05.720
It's a better fit for Mu Guiying,

00:26:05.720 --> 00:26:07.600
Yang Paifeng, and Bai Yunxian.

00:26:10.186 --> 00:26:11.762
Whatever they call me, it's still me.

00:26:11.880 --> 00:26:14.240
Even a Mo can't shut you up.

00:26:18.980 --> 00:26:20.780
(Qinchuan Qinqiang Opera Theater,
Popsicles)

00:26:20.800 --> 00:26:23.160
Popsicles! Get your popsicles!

00:26:23.920 --> 00:26:25.640
Popsicles for sale!

00:26:26.200 --> 00:26:28.560
(Qing: Chu Jiahe)
3 cents each.

00:27:30.080 --> 00:27:32.000
These out-of-towners are ruthless.

00:27:32.320 --> 00:27:34.160
They were just grooming each other

00:27:34.680 --> 00:27:37.240
before they bit over a bone.

00:27:45.080 --> 00:27:45.920
Sis,

00:27:46.280 --> 00:27:47.680
for tonight's performance,

00:27:47.680 --> 00:27:49.040
I'll be counting on you.

00:27:55.080 --> 00:27:57.040
Chu Jiahe, can you do this?

00:27:57.680 --> 00:27:58.760
Keep it steady!

00:28:03.680 --> 00:28:04.520
Jiahe,

00:28:04.960 --> 00:28:06.280
you're really bold.

00:28:06.600 --> 00:28:08.280
You've never played this part before.

00:28:09.120 --> 00:28:10.360
Can you handle it tonight?

00:28:11.200 --> 00:28:12.200
I've been waiting

00:28:13.040 --> 00:28:14.040
for this opportunity.

00:28:15.720 --> 00:28:16.960
I have to handle it tonight.

00:28:22.660 --> 00:28:24.860
(Qinchuan Province
Qinqiang Opera Theater)

00:28:30.040 --> 00:28:30.880
Sir,

00:28:31.920 --> 00:28:33.080
please open the gate.

00:28:33.080 --> 00:28:34.000
What are you doing?

00:28:34.600 --> 00:28:35.520
Let the car in.

00:28:38.560 --> 00:28:41.200
It's Yi Qin'e from Ningzhou.

00:28:41.400 --> 00:28:42.240
Who?

00:28:43.320 --> 00:28:45.360
Transfer order
and letter of introduction.

00:28:45.360 --> 00:28:47.500
(Transfer Order)

00:28:48.640 --> 00:28:49.480
This kid?

00:28:50.880 --> 00:28:52.360
Come on, sign in.

00:28:57.940 --> 00:29:01.140
(Shen Yun is ungrateful)

00:29:01.160 --> 00:29:03.600
Sir, let me sign in.

00:29:03.600 --> 00:29:04.560
Can I come in?

00:29:05.920 --> 00:29:07.680
(Visitor Log)
Whoever is reporting goes in.

00:29:08.920 --> 00:29:10.400
What about the luggage?

00:29:10.400 --> 00:29:11.760
Someone needs to take it inside.

00:29:11.760 --> 00:29:12.640
Luggage?

00:29:13.240 --> 00:29:15.080
Only one of you can help
with the luggage.

00:29:15.320 --> 00:29:16.160
I'll go.

00:29:17.840 --> 00:29:19.240
So eager.

00:29:22.240 --> 00:29:23.560
The office area is over here.

00:29:24.773 --> 00:29:25.680
Keep walking straight.

00:29:26.820 --> 00:29:27.700
I'll take it.

00:29:27.720 --> 00:29:28.560
I'll go with her.

00:29:30.360 --> 00:29:31.200
Okay.

00:29:32.840 --> 00:29:33.680
This way?

00:29:44.240 --> 00:29:45.413
The troupe leader's office.

00:29:46.480 --> 00:29:47.320
This is it.

00:29:54.280 --> 00:29:55.440
Why is the door locked?

00:30:03.800 --> 00:30:05.440
Such a big yard. Why is no one here?

00:30:07.960 --> 00:30:09.960
We should've told them we'd be late.

00:30:10.480 --> 00:30:11.320
Let's go.

00:30:12.920 --> 00:30:13.920
Is anyone here?

00:30:15.400 --> 00:30:16.440
Anyone here?

00:30:16.440 --> 00:30:19.900
(Office, Personnel Section)

00:30:26.360 --> 00:30:28.000
Why is the rehearsal hall empty too?

00:30:31.920 --> 00:30:33.560
Look how grand this rehearsal hall is.

00:30:35.920 --> 00:30:36.760
Look here.

00:30:37.960 --> 00:30:39.180
(Masters)
True Qinqiang Opera.

00:30:40.280 --> 00:30:41.760
The founder of modern Qinqiang Opera.

00:30:43.160 --> 00:30:45.360
You'll be in the same troupe
as them now.

00:31:00.600 --> 00:31:01.440
Who are you?

00:31:03.480 --> 00:31:06.960
We're from Ningzhou County Troupe

00:31:07.360 --> 00:31:08.260
for transfer paperwork.

00:31:08.260 --> 00:31:09.360
This is Yi Qin'e.

00:31:10.080 --> 00:31:11.200
And you are?

00:31:11.200 --> 00:31:12.080
I'm her uncle.

00:31:12.840 --> 00:31:14.226
Lead drummer of the County Troupe.

00:31:14.720 --> 00:31:15.680
You got transferred too?

00:31:16.040 --> 00:31:16.880
No.

00:31:16.891 --> 00:31:18.651
I just brought her here
to keep her company.

00:31:18.960 --> 00:31:20.480
Follow me to do the paperwork.

00:31:20.960 --> 00:31:22.480
When can I start rehearsing?

00:31:22.886 --> 00:31:23.720
After the paperwork,

00:31:23.720 --> 00:31:25.006
go back and wait for the notice.

00:31:25.340 --> 00:31:26.760
- Then...
- Where is the dorm?

00:31:27.720 --> 00:31:29.120
We have no dorms.

00:31:29.600 --> 00:31:30.680
No dorms?

00:31:30.680 --> 00:31:31.640
Where do people live?

00:31:32.000 --> 00:31:34.920
Hotels and the urban village are nearby.

00:31:34.920 --> 00:31:35.960
You can just rent a place.

00:31:35.960 --> 00:31:36.986
Chang'an City is so big.

00:31:36.997 --> 00:31:38.230
Can't you find a place to stay?

00:31:42.360 --> 00:31:44.440
That's how the clerks at the bottom are.

00:31:45.000 --> 00:31:46.173
Let's do the paperwork first.

00:31:46.640 --> 00:31:48.920
Wait till the troupe leader fixes him.

00:31:49.760 --> 00:31:50.800
What an attitude.

00:31:51.360 --> 00:31:52.720
Let's take a look over here.

00:31:53.190 --> 00:31:54.100
Hello, Hei.

00:31:54.120 --> 00:31:55.000
Going to school?

00:31:55.000 --> 00:31:55.840
Good, good.

00:31:57.520 --> 00:31:58.360
No.

00:31:59.400 --> 00:32:00.960
Whose kid is this? Slow down.

00:32:00.960 --> 00:32:02.400
Hei, have a bowl of noodles.

00:32:02.400 --> 00:32:03.240
I'll pass.

00:32:07.800 --> 00:32:09.600
Hei, let's play a round.

00:32:09.600 --> 00:32:10.440
No, no.

00:32:10.880 --> 00:32:12.200
Look, just a heads-up.

00:32:13.640 --> 00:32:14.560
They're cracking down.

00:32:14.560 --> 00:32:15.960
Be careful with the Mahjong Parlor.

00:32:16.440 --> 00:32:17.720
Stay sharp, Hei.

00:32:17.720 --> 00:32:18.560
Got it.

00:32:18.560 --> 00:32:19.720
- Have a smoke.
- No.

00:32:19.720 --> 00:32:21.280
- Take it.
- No.

00:32:22.760 --> 00:32:23.600
White Mo.

00:32:24.360 --> 00:32:25.360
Hei, have a Shaobing.

00:32:27.280 --> 00:32:28.120
Thanks.

00:32:28.920 --> 00:32:30.200
White Mo!

00:32:30.200 --> 00:32:33.500
(Wanted Notice)

00:32:33.720 --> 00:32:34.640
Alright, right here.

00:32:34.640 --> 00:32:35.560
Chief Qiao.

00:32:36.600 --> 00:32:37.840
What's going on here?

00:32:39.840 --> 00:32:41.000
A wanted notice.

00:32:41.920 --> 00:32:42.676
Our Diaojia Village

00:32:42.687 --> 00:32:43.640
has a lot of outsiders.

00:32:43.640 --> 00:32:45.080
The crowd here is quite mixed.

00:32:45.080 --> 00:32:46.680
Report any new issues to me ASAP.

00:32:47.280 --> 00:32:48.360
- A murderer.
- Is it over?

00:32:50.240 --> 00:32:51.080
I'm heading out.

00:32:53.040 --> 00:32:54.800
Wei Zhenhai.

00:33:00.560 --> 00:33:02.080
Leaving already?

00:33:02.680 --> 00:33:03.520
Yeah.

00:33:03.680 --> 00:33:05.240
Come back again soon!

00:33:05.240 --> 00:33:06.160
Okay, okay.

00:33:06.160 --> 00:33:07.000
Thanks.

00:33:13.480 --> 00:33:14.880
Where's that guy?

00:33:18.200 --> 00:33:19.120
The guy who brought you

00:33:19.840 --> 00:33:20.760
ran off.

00:33:21.200 --> 00:33:22.800
Ran off? Where to?

00:33:23.400 --> 00:33:24.520
Now, I understand.

00:33:25.120 --> 00:33:26.720
People can never withstand a test.

00:33:27.880 --> 00:33:28.720
It's meaningless.

00:33:30.040 --> 00:33:30.880
Pointless.

00:33:33.440 --> 00:33:34.360
Since it's pointless,

00:33:34.360 --> 00:33:35.360
why hold that?

00:33:35.360 --> 00:33:36.200
Why stand there?

00:33:38.200 --> 00:33:39.040
Right, right.

00:33:41.000 --> 00:33:41.840
It's good he left.

00:33:42.080 --> 00:33:43.680
We don't have to kick him out.

00:33:45.440 --> 00:33:46.560
Let's find a place first.

00:33:46.560 --> 00:33:48.360
We'll make do for tonight

00:33:49.000 --> 00:33:50.840
and look for Master Gu tomorrow.

00:34:03.280 --> 00:34:04.120
Uncle.

00:34:04.560 --> 00:34:05.400
Qin'e.

00:34:05.520 --> 00:34:07.080
Let's go watch the opera.

00:34:07.584 --> 00:34:08.888
(Qinchuan Qinqiang Opera Theater)

00:34:08.899 --> 00:34:13.290
ظآزFahai insists on being our enemyظآز

00:34:13.680 --> 00:34:14.920
It's already started.

00:34:15.280 --> 00:34:16.120
Come on, quick.

00:34:16.120 --> 00:34:16.960
Come on, come on.

00:34:17.150 --> 00:34:18.960
- ظآزNowظآز
- I heard tonight's show

00:34:18.960 --> 00:34:20.280
is Bai She Zhuan.

00:34:20.280 --> 00:34:23.560
- ظآزDriven apartظآز
- Front seats. How nice. Follow me.

00:34:23.560 --> 00:34:26.440
- ظآزSufferingظآز
- So, the troupe all came here.

00:34:26.440 --> 00:34:31.550
ظآزScared and full of endless sorrowظآز

00:34:31.550 --> 00:34:33.840
ظآزThe pain in my stomach is unbearableظآز

00:34:33.840 --> 00:34:36.070
ظآزI look around, with nowhere to goظآز

00:34:36.070 --> 00:34:39.520
ظآزSeeing the broken bridge
breaks my heartظآز

00:34:39.520 --> 00:34:42.920
ظآزHolding onظآز

00:34:46.850 --> 00:34:55.280
- ظآزQingظآز
- Ma'am, this is my seat.

00:34:55.280 --> 00:34:56.800
Sir, you took the wrong seat.

00:34:56.800 --> 00:34:57.640
This is my seat.

00:35:04.160 --> 00:35:05.040
Sit, sit.

00:35:08.930 --> 00:35:16.710
ظآزTowards the bridgeheadظآز

00:36:00.880 --> 00:36:04.080
- ظآزWalking onظآز
- Let them date!

00:36:04.080 --> 00:36:05.560
Why does Fahai always interfere?

00:36:05.560 --> 00:36:07.120
As if he knows anything about love.

00:36:08.160 --> 00:36:09.000
Keep it down.

00:36:12.000 --> 00:36:13.920
In 1924, Mr Lu Xun

00:36:13.920 --> 00:36:15.200
wrote an essay,

00:36:15.840 --> 00:36:18.080
On the Collapse of Leifeng Pagoda.

00:36:18.080 --> 00:36:19.280
He said the same thing.

00:36:20.080 --> 00:36:21.720
It reflects the masses' revolt

00:36:21.720 --> 00:36:24.440
- ظآزOn West Lakeظآز
- against feudalism.

00:36:28.240 --> 00:36:29.200
Did you hear that?

00:36:29.200 --> 00:36:32.520
- ظآزNear Broken Bridge Pavilionظآز
- Great audience.

00:36:32.520 --> 00:36:33.760
This is Chang'an.

00:36:39.610 --> 00:36:40.510
Xu Xian!

00:36:58.190 --> 00:36:59.130
Qing!

00:37:09.040 --> 00:37:10.000
Bravo!

00:37:10.000 --> 00:37:11.860
- Why deceive my sister
- Bravo!

00:37:11.860 --> 00:37:14.340
and sneak to Jinshan Temple?

00:37:15.470 --> 00:37:17.600
Tell me!

00:37:19.990 --> 00:37:21.150
Speak!

00:37:22.490 --> 00:37:23.500
Qing, this...

00:37:23.500 --> 00:37:24.850
This was all Fahai...

00:37:24.850 --> 00:37:25.700
Shut up!

00:37:26.380 --> 00:37:28.120
If you hadn't believed Fahai's lies,

00:37:28.120 --> 00:37:30.330
how would my sister
have suffered so much?

00:37:30.330 --> 00:37:31.920
You ingrate!

00:37:31.920 --> 00:37:34.100
Why even keep you alive?

00:37:34.100 --> 00:37:35.020
Dear!

00:37:35.800 --> 00:37:36.740
Honey!

00:37:48.480 --> 00:37:49.799
What's wrong with Chu Jiahe today?

00:37:50.080 --> 00:37:50.920
Is she crazy?

00:37:51.600 --> 00:37:53.760
Qing's moves are unreal today.

00:37:54.146 --> 00:37:55.732
She doesn't even look like she's acting.

00:37:56.810 --> 00:37:57.750
Qing.

00:38:08.520 --> 00:38:09.520
What are you doing?

00:38:09.520 --> 00:38:10.360
Are you crazy?

00:38:18.520 --> 00:38:20.000
Bravo!

00:38:24.960 --> 00:38:25.800
Bravo!

00:38:26.600 --> 00:38:27.520
Uncle.

00:38:27.520 --> 00:38:29.600
Chu Jiahe is playing Qing.

00:38:31.720 --> 00:38:33.080
The Chu Jiahe from your class?

00:38:33.520 --> 00:38:34.800
She made it here first.

00:38:36.160 --> 00:38:37.520
She's completely transformed.

00:38:38.840 --> 00:38:40.120
The stage is so beautiful.

00:38:40.600 --> 00:38:41.920
They sing so well.

00:38:42.480 --> 00:38:44.480
You'll be the next one up there.

00:38:46.640 --> 00:38:48.400
Uncle, Qin'e.

00:38:48.400 --> 00:38:49.240
Let's go.

00:38:49.600 --> 00:38:51.400
What's the rush? Show some manners.

00:38:52.040 --> 00:38:53.280
Show some respect for actors.

00:39:00.640 --> 00:39:02.880
Where did the provincial troupe put you?

00:39:14.600 --> 00:39:15.440
Look!

00:39:16.360 --> 00:39:17.440
That's the City Wall ahead.

00:39:18.200 --> 00:39:19.640
Behind it is the Bell Tower.

00:39:20.120 --> 00:39:21.600
Further ahead is the Drum Tower.

00:39:22.000 --> 00:39:23.480
This is the main road of Chang'an.

00:39:24.840 --> 00:39:25.840
Further ahead

00:39:25.840 --> 00:39:26.880
is Huimin Street.

00:39:27.600 --> 00:39:29.640
Chang'an has so many snacks.

00:39:30.800 --> 00:39:31.846
Half are on Huimin Street.

00:39:33.040 --> 00:39:34.680
And it gets livelier at night.

00:39:51.250 --> 00:39:52.760
Listen, you weren't good before.

00:39:52.760 --> 00:39:53.560
How nice.

00:39:53.571 --> 00:39:54.800
- I was wrong.
- That's great.

00:39:54.800 --> 00:39:56.220
Did you see the audience's reaction?

00:39:56.800 --> 00:39:58.120
Why are you crying?

00:39:58.120 --> 00:39:59.760
This is how you build a character.

00:39:59.760 --> 00:40:01.160
You all should learn from this.

00:40:01.160 --> 00:40:04.120
This is the Qing I envisioned!

00:40:04.680 --> 00:40:05.600
Chu Jiahe!

00:40:05.600 --> 00:40:06.520
Where is Chu Jiahe?

00:40:06.520 --> 00:40:08.000
I didn't see her when I went down.

00:40:08.000 --> 00:40:09.640
Guess she was tired and went back.

00:40:10.920 --> 00:40:12.520
Director Feng, she's crazy!

00:40:12.520 --> 00:40:13.360
Chu Jiahe!

00:40:13.840 --> 00:40:14.680
Where's Chu Jiahe?

00:40:14.760 --> 00:40:15.600
He's with hammers.

00:40:15.720 --> 00:40:17.000
You must be crazy!

00:40:17.000 --> 00:40:18.960
This isn't acting; it's murder!

00:40:19.280 --> 00:40:20.840
I have no grudge against you!

00:40:21.440 --> 00:40:22.960
Every strike was aimed at me!

00:40:22.960 --> 00:40:24.120
You even kicked me twice!

00:40:24.760 --> 00:40:25.600
Fahai!

00:40:26.000 --> 00:40:27.560
Subdue Chu Jiahe for me!

00:40:27.560 --> 00:40:28.720
Subdue Qing!

00:40:29.240 --> 00:40:30.160
Where is Chu Jiahe?

00:40:31.360 --> 00:40:32.720
Have you seen Chu Jiahe?

00:40:32.720 --> 00:40:34.040
No.

00:40:34.140 --> 00:40:40.500
(Diaojia Village)

00:41:23.420 --> 00:41:24.860
(Qinqiang opera: Bai She Zhuan)

00:41:42.620 --> 00:41:48.340
(Beishan Government Office in Chang'an)

00:41:53.680 --> 00:41:55.600
This is our Beishan office in Chang'an.

00:41:55.960 --> 00:41:57.760
It's our own place, very convenient.

00:41:57.760 --> 00:41:58.600
Come on in.

00:41:58.600 --> 00:42:00.240
(Reception)

00:42:00.240 --> 00:42:02.400
Three rooms with bathrooms, please.

00:42:02.400 --> 00:42:03.260
Hongbing.

00:42:03.260 --> 00:42:04.270
- Come on.
- Come here.

00:42:04.270 --> 00:42:06.120
No, we don't need bathrooms.

00:42:06.120 --> 00:42:07.440
Standard rooms are fine.

00:42:07.440 --> 00:42:09.000
Two rooms are enough.

00:42:09.600 --> 00:42:10.760
How much for a night?

00:42:11.280 --> 00:42:12.240
Uncle, why?

00:42:12.240 --> 00:42:13.160
You're embarrassing me.

00:42:13.600 --> 00:42:14.700
If you don't let me pay,

00:42:14.711 --> 00:42:15.951
we won't stay here. We'll leave.

00:42:18.160 --> 00:42:19.080
Just book it then.

00:42:19.080 --> 00:42:20.720
- Two rooms.
- Okay.

00:42:21.680 --> 00:42:23.600
Preferably far apart.

00:42:23.600 --> 00:42:25.660
- Different floors are fine.
- Okay.

00:42:25.680 --> 00:42:27.480
Uncle, what are you doing?

00:42:28.720 --> 00:42:29.646
None of your business.

00:42:29.920 --> 00:42:30.920
Who should I listen to?

00:42:31.240 --> 00:42:32.610
- Listen to me.
- Alright.

00:42:33.840 --> 00:42:35.120
Are Rooms 205 and 309 okay?

00:42:35.400 --> 00:42:36.280
Yes.

00:42:36.280 --> 00:42:37.120
Alright.

00:42:37.489 --> 00:42:38.589
Any letter of introduction?

00:42:38.600 --> 00:42:39.480
Yes.

00:42:39.520 --> 00:42:40.360
Here you go.

00:42:41.440 --> 00:42:42.760
How much for one night?

00:42:42.760 --> 00:42:43.600
One fifty.

00:42:45.040 --> 00:42:46.200
Alright, go to sleep now.

00:42:46.200 --> 00:42:47.440
Make sure to lock the door.

00:42:53.600 --> 00:42:54.640
Is Qin'e asleep yet?

00:42:55.520 --> 00:42:57.120
Mind your own business. Go to bed.

00:43:05.020 --> 00:43:06.940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

00:43:09.400 --> 00:43:10.840
Doufunao, Youtiao.

00:43:10.840 --> 00:43:12.600
- I've got everything.
- Okay.

00:43:12.880 --> 00:43:13.720
I have more.

00:43:13.720 --> 00:43:15.160
Just seeing him gets on my nerves.

00:43:15.171 --> 00:43:16.320
I don't even know what to do.

00:43:16.320 --> 00:43:18.560
Only the lead gets a house.

00:43:19.000 --> 00:43:20.400
The cast list for You Xi Hu.

00:43:20.480 --> 00:43:21.800
(Yi Qin'e: Role F)
She's an F?

00:43:21.960 --> 00:43:23.520
That's nothing but a walk-on.

00:43:23.520 --> 00:43:25.400
Don't you worry. I've got your back.

00:43:27.400 --> 00:43:28.920
What are you doing? Stop it!

00:43:29.120 --> 00:43:31.160
Gu, what are you doing?

00:43:31.680 --> 00:43:33.000
I couldn't stop them.

00:43:37.000 --> 00:43:41.620
ظآزWhen I woke up and turned backظآز

00:43:43.090 --> 00:43:47.930
ظآزI wasn't sure where to goظآز

00:43:49.370 --> 00:43:53.560
ظآزWe met and brushed pastظآز

00:43:55.120 --> 00:44:02.420
ظآزYour shadow drifted out of sightظآز

00:44:16.790 --> 00:44:20.540
ظآزThe stove fire blazed in my dreamظآز

00:44:22.140 --> 00:44:27.710
ظآزLit up the tracks of pearly tearsظآز

00:44:28.830 --> 00:44:32.890
ظآزIn my dream, water sleeves flewظآز

00:44:34.020 --> 00:44:39.610
ظآزHiding a lifetime of loveظآز

00:44:40.770 --> 00:44:44.970
ظآزThe Qinling Mountains
crossed the stageظآز

00:44:46.010 --> 00:44:51.640
ظآزSpring water brewed strong wineظآز

00:44:52.810 --> 00:44:57.500
ظآزSheep moved through the valleyظآز

00:44:58.180 --> 00:45:03.350
ظآزIt felt like a promise
from another lifeظآز

00:45:04.020 --> 00:45:09.050
ظآزWhen I woke up and turned backظآز

00:45:10.080 --> 00:45:15.510
ظآزI wasn't sure where to goظآز

00:45:15.890 --> 00:45:21.170
ظآزIf I chose again, I'd still roamظآز

00:45:22.120 --> 00:45:27.930
ظآزAll over this sunlit plateauظآز

00:45:27.930 --> 00:45:33.350
ظآزThe dream ends; the curtain fallsظآز

00:45:33.900 --> 00:45:39.410
ظآزMoonlight washes off this stage makeupظآز

00:45:39.960 --> 00:45:44.920
ظآزThe one in the mirror wears gray hairظآز

00:45:45.940 --> 00:45:51.220
ظآزAlready sang all my joy and sorrowظآز

00:45:52.020 --> 00:46:01.050
ظآزAlready shouted across Qinchuan Plainظآز